high_descs: Turn left and take one step, then turn right and take one step, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the apple that is on the counter.
Turn right and walk across the room, then turn left.
Open the microwave and put the apple inside, then turn the microwave on for three seconds, then open the microwave door and pick up the apple.
Turn left and walk to the stove, then turn left and take two steps, then turn right.
Put the apple in the fridge.
Go forward, turn left when reach counter with apple on it.
Turn right, go to wall, turn left to face microwave.
Open microwave, put apple in, close door.  Wait three seconds, open microwave, remove apple, close door.
Open refrigerator, put apple on third shelf down in refrigerator, close refrigerator door.
anns.task_desc: Heat apple in microwave, put it in refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn left then turn right walk forward then face the counter on your left
Pick up the pear on the counter
Turn right and head to the microwave on your left
Open the microwave put in and out the pear then close the microwave
Turn left and head to the fridge
Open the fridge and put in the pear then close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put the heated pear in the fridge
